title: @Riot Help pls.

embed.description: The easy way to save screenshots, GIFs, and websites. Make everyone happy by sharing smarter, faster, and with your point crystal clear.

body: Im lvl 30 and i own almost all champions but it says those are the reasons for which I cannot play ranked. :( Also    Im gold 4... so I have played ranked like.. 2-3 hours ago.

replies.body:
It seems for some reason the server wasn't identifying you as eligible for ranked play. It looks like it's been resolved now, though, so I wish you the best in your ranked matches!

If you have any other issues with this, I recommend [submitting a ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so our account specialists can investigate further.
